import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['home_score'] = pd.to_numeric(data['home_score'], errors='ignore')
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['home_score'], bins=20)
    plt.xlabel('Home Scores')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of home scores?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.xticks(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['away_score'] = pd.to_numeric(data['away_score'], errors='coerce')
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['away_score'], bins=20)
    plt.xlabel('Away Scores')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of away scores?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.xticks(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['score_diff'] = data['home_score'] - data['away_score']
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['score_diff'], bins=20, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Score Difference')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the difference between home and away scores?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.xticks(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    matches_by_division = data.groupby('division').size().reset_index(name='matches')
    matches_by_division = matches_by_division.sort_values(by='matches', ascending=False)
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    ax = plt.bar(matches_by_division['division'], matches_by_division['matches'])
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of matches played by division?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
